OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cwoman found dead in Newport
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for information
OL,7,Fafter the death of a woman in Newport.
OL,9,FOfficers from Gwent Police, including
OL,10,Fspecially trained firearms officers,
OL,11,Fattended a report of an altercation
OL,12,Foutside a property in St Vincent Road,
OL,13,FNewport, in the early hours of
OL,14,FSaturday 18th July.
OL,16,FA woman, who has not been formally
OL,17,Fidentified, was pronounced dead by
OL,18,Fparamedics a short distance away, near
OL,19,FChepstow Road. Her family has been
OL,20,Finformed.
