OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cwoman found dead in Newport
OL,6,FA 66-year-old man from Newport, is
OL,7,Fcurrently in police custody after
OL,8,Fbeing arrested on suspicion of murder.
OL,10,FChief Superintendent John Davies said:
OL,11,F"We understand that reports of this
OL,12,Fnature are deeply unsettling and
OL,13,Fdistressing for our communities. A
OL,14,Fman, who was arrested at the scene, is
OL,15,Fcurrently in police custody, and we
OL,16,Fare not looking for anyone else in
OL,17,Fconnection with the death.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
