OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1784623688
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cwoman found dead in Newport
OL,6,F"There will be an increased police
OL,7,Fpresence in the area, while our
OL,8,Fofficers continue to carry out
OL,9,Fenquiries. If you have any concerns or
OL,10,Fhave any information, please don't
OL,11,Fhesitate to speak to them."
OL,13,FGwent Police have asked anyone with
OL,14,Finformation, including CCTV or dashcam
OL,15,Ffootage between the hours of 1am and
OL,16,F3am on Saturday 18 July to contact
OL,17,Fthem.
